VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT KeyGenParameterSpec\.Builder\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:setUserAuthenticationRequired\s*\(\s*true|setUserAuthenticationParameters|setUnlockedDeviceRequired\s*\(\s*true
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Android KeyStore key generation that does not require user authentication before the key is usable.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Android KeyStore Key Without User Authentication Binding.
